        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真无线重低音头戴耳机，两种重低音模式比较 + 性价比高 + 续航力高</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony ULT WEAR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WH-ULT900N]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1242758</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 早前推出全新头戴式无线降噪耳机 ULT WEAR，ULT WEAR 属次旗舰级别耳机，在耳机位置加入了 ULT 按键，可供用家切换两种重低音模式。ULT WEAR 有齐音色、主动降噪、3D 头部追踪音效、DSEE 数码音质升技术等旗舰耳机拥有的功能，而定价只有旗舰耳机约一半，绝对抵玩！事不宜迟，即刻开箱评测。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243117 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>黑白</strong><strong>灰三</strong><strong>色</strong><strong> 低调设计不易留痕</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 的设计及外观颇为简洁，耳机侧面印有细小雷射反光的 Sony 字样，低调设计同时不乏个性。机身用上了磨砂质地，摸上手舒适，不易留下指纹等污渍。ULT WEAR 有 3 款颜色选择，小编拿到的是黑色，型格之选。另外还有灰白色和森林灰色，感觉比较优雅高贵，更会适合女士。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243118 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 的设计及外观简洁，机身用上了磨砂质地，摸上手舒适，不易留下指纹等污渍</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243119 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机侧面印有细小雷射反光的 Sony 字样</p><h2><strong>耳罩不重</strong> <strong>佩戴感舒适</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 包装附送了 1 个收纳袋，里面有 1 条 USB-C 充电线及 1 条 3.5mm 线。ULT WEAR 是头罩式耳机，机身只重 255 克，小编戴了 2 小时感觉实净，耳罩用料记忆绵，亦不会轻易掉下，耳罩尺寸刚好，未有太大局促感。但如要将耳机挂颈，感觉就有点不舒服，不太适合长时间挂颈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243122 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 包装附送了 1 个收纳袋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243123 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲里面有 1 条 USB-C 充电线及 1 条 3.5mm 线</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243121 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩尺寸刚好，未有太大局促感</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243124 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲但如要将耳机挂颈，感觉就有点不舒服</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　介面快速评测 + 开卖详情公布</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活跃玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事业的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>保留</strong><strong>实体键</strong> <strong>「</strong><strong>ULT</strong><strong>」增强低音</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 保留了一部份实体键，而未有采用完全轻触式设计，还原实体键的直接感，可减少误触的风险。所有实体键集中在左耳罩，操控方面颇为简单，最底在 USB-C 充电口旁的按键是开关掣，可用作蓝牙配对或开关。旁边有切换主动降噪及环境声按键。值得一提，ULT WEAR 新增了一个「ULT」按键，可供用家切换重低音模式及重低音增强模式，切换时耳机会发出提示声。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243126 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最底在 USB-C 充电口旁的按键是开关掣，可用作蓝牙配对或开关，旁边有切换主动降噪及环境声按键</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243125 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 新增了一个「ULT」按键，可供用家切换重低音模式及重低音增强模式，切换时耳机会发出提示声</p><h2><strong>Sony Headphones</strong> <strong>自定义</strong> <strong>EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 向来都有自家应用程式，用家可以下载 Headphones ，调整主动降噪、通透模式、EQ 等。EQ 方面就预设 10 项，分别是「欢快」、「激昂」、「醇美」、「放松」、「声乐」、「强化高音」、「强化重音」、「演说」、「手动」及 2 项自订。用家亦可按下设定图示，选择「ULT 1」、「ULT 2」或「ULT OFF」开启或关闭重低音及重低音增强，同时可选择增强的程度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243129 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243130 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以下载 Headphones ，调整主动降噪、通透模式、EQ 等</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243131 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲EQ 方面就预设 10 项，分别是「欢快」、「激昂」、「醇美」等，及 2 项自订</p><h2><strong>多装置连接，非常方便实用</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 有多装置连接，用家可同时连上电脑及手机，小编工作时经常不止用一个装置，所以觉得这功能非常实用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243132 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可多装置连接</p><h2>通透模式有惊喜</h2><p>ULT WEAR 使用了降风噪结构，耳机内外都具备双噪音感应器，加上 V1 整合处理器，可以有效捕捉及隔绝环境声。小编特别欣赏其环境声，清晰之余亦相对自然，不似其他耳机仍有一定的局促感，ULT WEAR 收音也未见刻意放大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243133 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编特别欣赏其环境声，清晰之余亦相对自然</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　介面快速评测 + 开卖详情公布</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活跃玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事业的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>支援快速充电，充电</strong> <strong>3 分钟可用 90 </strong><strong>分钟</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">续航力方面，充满电的 ULT WEAR 最多可以连续使用 50 小时，超长的使用时间足够小编用 4 至 5 日。ULT WEAR 支援快速充电，只要充电 3 分钟，即可使用 90 分钟，充电 10 分钟更可使用 5 小时，可谓是惊人。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243135 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 支援快速充电，只要充电 3 分钟，即可使用 90 分钟</p><h2><strong>音场阔，适合强调低音的流行曲</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 可使用 LDAC 制式，加上使用了 40mm 动圈单元，加强了耳机的低频处理。小编在 Sony XPERIA 上使用 MOOV 播放 Mr. 的《黑色狂迷》，歌曲属于摇滚乐，编曲比较复杂但 ULT WEAR 在低频上更提升一个层次，「UTL」功能提供了足够份量及下潜力，惟分析力中等，在处理编曲复杂的歌曲未太称心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243136 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Mr.《黑色狂迷》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">谢安琪的《十二月二十二》录音版本。明显听到音场阔、听到歌曲细节。惟歌曲将人声靠前，高频及人声声音突出，与 ULT WEAR 耳机特点相违背，不太强调人声及高频，用家需透过调较 EQ 方可获得更清澈的高频人声。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243137 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲谢安琪《十二月二十二》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">再听听黄耀明的《身外情》，歌曲开头已有低沉的低音结他，ULT WEAR 都展现出处理低频的能力，低音结他的下潜力强劲，是刻意强调低音，却不致于失去平衡，反而升华了歌曲本身的特色。高频音色方面未是 ULT WEAR 的强项，但亦恰到好处。整体来说，ULT WEAR 音场阔，适合收听强调低音的流行曲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243138 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲黄耀明《身外情》</p><h2>两种重低音效果比较</h2><p>以 Mr.《黑色狂迷》为例，摇滚乐开启重低音模式的确比关闭更适合，重低音加强了歌曲的节奏感，但小编认为「UTL 1」已足够，使用「UTL 2」反而会使有点低频过于用力，失去了应有平衡。用家亦可在 Headphones 等化器中微调重低音的份量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243167 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可在 Headphones 等化器中微调重低音的份量</p><h2><strong>总结：</strong><strong>低频强劲</strong> <strong>续航力够</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 的售价为 HK$ 1599，属中价位，在功能上都拍得住旗舰耳机，又有强劲低频音色，再加上续航力达 50 小时。价钱只需一半旗舰耳机的约一半，性价比极高，适合喜欢听低频的使用者。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　介面快速评测 + 开卖详情公布</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活跃玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事业的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/">【评测】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真无线重低音头戴耳机，两种重低音模式比较 + 性价比高 + 续航力高</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
